00:40:16.810 --> 00:40:19.320
I've been very pleased so far.

00:40:19.320 --> 00:40:22.240
My question for you is, is
there a place for mindlessness

00:40:22.240 --> 00:40:23.200
in the day to day?

00:40:23.200 --> 00:40:27.810
I know mindfulness is kind of
