00:40:27.810 --> 00:40:29.620
it as this superior
state of being.

00:40:29.620 --> 00:40:32.360
But I guess, is there a
place from alternating

00:40:32.360 --> 00:40:34.300
between the two, or
should one always try

00:40:34.300 --> 00:40:36.829
to be mindful whenever possible?

00:40:36.829 --> 00:40:38.370
Because I feel like,
at least for me,

00:40:38.370 --> 00:40:40.120
it's kind of
difficult to maintain

00:40:40.120 --> 00:40:42.201
this always mindful state.

00:40:42.201 --> 00:40:43.700
DAVID GELLES: It's
a great question,

00:40:43.700 --> 00:40:45.470
and it's absolutely hard.

00:40:45.470 --> 00:40:47.460
And I think it's not
realistic to expect

00:40:47.460 --> 00:40:49.820
ourselves to be always mindful.

00:40:49.820 --> 00:40:54.480
I guess what I'd say is
I would try not to create

00:40:54.480 --> 00:40:58.370
such a polarization and such a
dichotomy between mindfulness

00:40:58.370 --> 00:41:01.470
as this kind of paradigm
of healthy living,

00:41:01.470 --> 00:41:07.580
and whatever is not mindfulness
as some reckless state.

00:41:07.580 --> 00:41:10.920
I think the nature of
the mind is to wander.

00:41:10.920 --> 00:41:14.730
And the nature of the mind is
to be intrigued by stimulus

00:41:14.730 --> 00:41:16.480
and to want to check
our smartphones.

00:41:16.480 --> 00:41:19.840
And I'm not suggesting that
we stop doing any of that.

00:41:19.840 --> 00:41:21.770
I think what
mindfulness meditators

00:41:21.770 --> 00:41:26.100
advocate is that by training our
attention, by giving ourselves

00:41:26.100 --> 00:41:30.500
the ability, the potential,
the willpower, essentially,

00:41:30.500 --> 00:41:32.960
to bring ourselves back to
the present moment in very

00:41:32.960 --> 00:41:37.960
deliberate ways, good things
can happen in those moments.

00:41:37.960 --> 00:41:44.250
So I love the
question, and I think--

00:41:44.250 --> 00:41:47.650
I want to consider a more
fulsome answer ultimately.

00:41:47.650 --> 00:41:51.019
But I guess I would start
by trying not to perpetuate

00:41:51.019 --> 00:41:52.560
this myth that
mindfulness is somehow

00:41:52.560 --> 00:41:55.240
this elevated
state that suggests

00:41:55.240 --> 00:42:00.340
every other way of
being is inferior.

