my book, which I think

00:43:17.470 --> 00:43:20.760
is a valid kind of
path of inquiry.

00:43:20.760 --> 00:43:23.610
I think it's important
to address the skeptics,

00:43:23.610 --> 00:43:27.720
even if to wholehandedly
dismiss them.

00:43:27.720 --> 00:43:28.780
And so I did that.

00:43:28.780 --> 00:43:30.660
And then I also kind
