Thank you for coming.

00:48:26.984 --> 00:48:29.700
I had a question specifically
about the meditation part.

00:48:29.700 --> 00:48:33.610
Once you decide to set aside
that time, what have you found

00:48:33.610 --> 00:48:36.860
is effective for not
actually just continuing

00:48:36.860 --> 00:48:38.865
those practices of either
dwelling on the past

00:48:38.865 --> 00:48:40.240
or just worrying
about the future

00:48:40.240 --> 00:48:42.552
and just carrying that same
behavior into that time

00:48:42.552 --> 00:48:43.510
that you've carved out.

00:48:43.510 --> 00:48:47.490
So are there recommended phrases
you're supposed to meditate on?

00:48:47.490 --> 00:48:50.200
Or how do you recommend not
just doing the same thing,

00:48:50.200 --> 00:48:52.160
but just sitting down
in a quieter space.

00:48:52.160 --> 00:48:52.951
DAVID GELLES: Yeah.

00:48:52.951 --> 00:48:54.590
It's hard, no doubt about.

00:48:54.590 --> 00:48:57.240
Mindfulness meditation
is, I should add,

00:48:57.240 --> 00:48:59.554
one of a variety of
meditative techniques.

00:48:59.554 --> 00:49:00.970
There's transcendental
meditation.

00:49:00.970 --> 00:49:02.490
There's mantra meditations.

00:49:02.490 --> 00:49:04.680
So mindfulness meditation
doesn't necessarily

00:49:04.680 --> 00:49:06.510
use any phrases.

00:49:06.510 --> 00:49:10.380
Instead, the goal,
essentially, the practice

00:49:10.380 --> 00:49:13.570
is just finding those moments,
essentially remembering.

00:49:13.570 --> 00:49:18.010
And actually, that's one
Sanskrit interpretation

00:49:18.010 --> 00:49:18.515
of the word.

00:49:18.515 --> 00:49:19.890
The Sanskrit word
for mindfulness

00:49:19.890 --> 00:49:21.840
is actually remembering--
so remembering

00:49:21.840 --> 00:49:26.160
to come back to the present
moment over and over and over.

00:49:26.160 --> 00:49:28.120
I wish I had a shortcut,
but what I would say

00:49:28.120 --> 00:49:30.416
is it doesn't have to
be five minutes or 30

00:49:30.416 --> 00:49:32.415
minutes every day for an
extended period, amount

00:49:32.415 --> 00:49:33.160
of time.

00:49:33.160 --> 00:49:34.701
I was talking to
[INAUDIBLE] earlier.

00:49:34.701 --> 00:49:37.720
It's the short moments many
times throughout the day--

00:49:37.720 --> 00:49:41.280
can be just as impactful
as a month-long retreat,

00:49:41.280 --> 00:49:42.219
for example.

